### TABLEDATA

CREATE TABLE user_profiles (
  user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  username VARCHAR(50),
  email VARCHAR(100),
  age INT,
  gender VARCHAR(10)
);

CREATE TABLE user_interactions (
  interaction_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id INT,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP,
  action VARCHAR(50),
  item_id INT
);

CREATE TABLE product_recommendations (
  recommendation_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id INT,
  recommended_item_id INT,
  score FLOAT,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

### STATEMENT

UPDATE user_profiles SET age = 30 WHERE user_id = 1;
